nodes.text: Yub Yub: Meet the Ewoks from Endor

Yub Yub: Meet the Ewoks from Endor was a blog post detailing the various Ewoks seen in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, as well as the two spin-off Ewok movies and the Ewoks television show. The post was written by Tim Veekhoven and published on StarWars.com on October 29, 2014.
